    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK518">
<l>viṉaikkurimai nāṭiya piṉṟai yavaṉai</l>
<l>yataṟkuriya ṉākac ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having considered what work a man is fit for, let (the king) employ him in that work.</l>
            </lg>
